data.description:
WATER VIEW home in a well sought resort style community!  NEWER ROOF AND IMPACT WINDOWS!!! WALKING DISTANCE TO SCHOOLS AND SPLASH PARK FOR KIDS TO ENJOY! Fireplace in the family room. Screen enclosed patio.  Open floor plan.  All appliances stay including Refrigerator, washer and dryer.
Close to NAS JAX, brand new Baptist Clay Hospital, shopping, restaurants, Clay county Public Library, Fresh Market, Publix, Super Walmart, Target, etc. A MUST SEE!!!
